    "This could explain why, in DG, the network pays more attention to this modality.",
    "In addition, the availability of target data in UDA enables L RNA to improve the balance between the norms of the different modalities, so that the model can better use the contributions of each modality to make its final decisions.",
    "This improved mutual contribution between modalities (reflected in the increased accuracy reported in Table 2) may explain the (relatively) lower norm of Flow in UDA, which is balanced by increased norms of (i.e., attention to) the other two modalities (RGB and Audio).",
